INSERT INTO `tsys_config` (`type`,`ckey`,`cvalue`,`updater`,`update_datetime`,`remark`,`company_code`,`system_code`) VALUES ('sys_txt','red_packet_rule_EN','<p>Rules of red packet</p><p>Red packet is a application developed by\r\nTHA wallet， rules are as following：</p><p>1. The amount of a single red packet sent\r\nshould between 0.001 - 1000000 (one million) digital currency</p><p>2. The amount of red packet is limited\r\nbetween 1-100</p><p>3. Random packet，the number\r\nof received packets is random，the one who receive the most is the Luckiest draw</p><p>4.Identical packet the number of received\r\npackets is Identical</p><p>5.New users who receive the red packet will\r\nautomatically become apprentices of the sender </p><p>6.Received digital currency will\r\nautomatically be deposited into the personal wallet</p><p>7.Red envelopes not opened within 24 hours\r\nwill automatically return to the sender\'s personal wallet</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Official account</p><p>Official website：thachain.org</p><p>Email address：<a href=\"mailto:official@thachain.org\">official@thachain.org</a></p><p>Telegram Chinese community：<a href=\"https://t.me/THAWallet_cn\">https://t.me/THAWallet_cn</a></p><p>l&nbsp; Telegram English community：<a href=\"https://t.me/THAWallet_en\">https://t.me/THAWallet_en</a></p><p>Sina weibo：<a href=\"http://weibo.com/THAWallet\">http://weibo.com/THAWallet</a></p><p>l&nbsp; Twitter：@THAWallet</p><p>l&nbsp; Facebook：@THAWallet</p><p>Wechat official account：</p><p><img src=\"http://pajvine9a.bkt.clouddn.com/图片 1_1533114570198.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"><br></p><p><br></p>','admin',now(),'红包规则（英文）','CD-TOKEN00018','CD-TOKEN00018');
